WWE-TNA-ROH-Diva Diaries with Candice LeRae DVDRip x264-NoNeYa

Diva Diaries
with Candice LeRae

On this episode of Diva Diaries, Sojo Bolt sits down with one half of the World's Cutest Tag Team, Candice LeRae. 
Unlike a lot of other girls, Candice grew up idolizing "Macho Man" Randy Savage. Joey Ryan may not be a stand 
in for Miss Elizabeth, but he has been a big part of Candice's journey in pro wrestling.

The biggest step in that journey was getting Candice on the Pro Wrestling Guerrilla roster. 
Her PWG career has been quite a story; She reflects on her days of managing Human Tornado all the way to the top
with World's Cutest Tag Team's reign as PWG tag team champions. Candice isn't just a big deal in Reseda,
her effect on inter gender wrestling has changed the way women are used on independent wrestling shows 
across the country. Candice rarely does interviews, but here she is very open and honest.

She is also willing to answer her critics who feel the inter gender wrestling is a fad and it doesn't draw any money. 
So, sit back and continue to be amazed by Candice LeRae on this edition of Diva Diaries.
